{"tid":783262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"舞台「臉超臭、失誤」？不只YERI連IRENE","createTime":"2018-08-17T11:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T17:03:03.000Z","uid":51412,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ff19e36fc47492f8b603bc205508ad812f436c14","tid":783262,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"舞台「臉超臭、失誤」？不只YERI連IRENE都被批「傷了粉絲的心」<br />\n<br />\n連粉絲都說舞台沒誠意、很傷心啊...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yBOUowiNJw0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyBOUowiNJw0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2RykbzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=51596cfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yBOUowiNJw0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\nSM家不只以外貌，每一團都有超整齊的舞蹈<br />\n讓人感嘆不僅顏值高，實力也強<br />\n但Red Velvet的成員YERI卻常被指出舞蹈缺失<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MJ6DV0xu0p0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMJ6DV0xu0p0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2RykbzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6c768987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MJ6DV0xu0p0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n被說練習量不足、拍子不對<br />\n表情管理欠佳<br />\n跟成員比起來更明顯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CATzR4PvCJo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCATzR4PvCJo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2RykbzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=26067dc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CATzR4PvCJo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n不只網友、連粉絲們都留言<br />\n「就只是沒練習吧，SM沒有舞蹈老師嗎？完全按照自己的意思跳，要合團隊啊」<br />\n「從以前開始就不會跳，多練習吧！」<br />\n「《Russian Roulette》開始就動作很小，不知從何開始變成連拍子都對不上...」<br />\n「誠意不足大概跳的感覺」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SjzSdAuQBiI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSjzSdAuQBiI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2RykbzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7ea1c6ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SjzSdAuQBiI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n不只YERI<br />\n最近IRENE也因為這個影片讓網友和粉絲認為&quot;不敬業&quot;<br />\n(一分鐘開始)<br />\n<br />\n「身為粉絲每次看到指責舞蹈的文章想要反駁<br />\n但除了WENDY、SEULGI其他成員舞蹈都越來越敷衍」<br />\n「看起來當IDOL當到很煩的表情」<br />\n「雖然IRENE跳了數千數萬次，但也要為了看三分鐘舞台而從遙遠的地方來看的粉絲著想吧！」<br />\n<br />\n「原來是簽名會的舞台啊...以為是排演的影片」<br />\n「得藝人病了吧！」<br />\n「挖真的是外貌至上主義讓人生氣啊！Wendy這麼認真的人卻沒IRENE如此受到關注」<br />\n「失去初心了吧！以前都不會這樣的」<br />\n<br />\n也有網友緩頰認為<br />\n「應該是因為中暑了吧...」<br />\n「還是身體不舒服？」<br />\n「公司把行程排太滿才這樣的吧」<br />\n<br />\n當偶像不僅外貌、表情要管理好、體力更是重要啊！<br />\n大家怎麼看呢？"},{"pid":"9db4fe5ef2c668bdd8acd31e2054e4f35e45cb17","tid":783262,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9b19e959fa1065e8518c9dbe8503f2b08ac5ee","tid":783262,"uid":177639,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"行程密 太累"},{"pid":"cb8561e5d8347c510e0fb92a00e5da6792175bf2","tid":783262,"uid":88491,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"以為比金仔渣住枝槍迫佢跳"},{"pid":"089fb38e370493cac53cd2d0655e8fa5d537b8fb","tid":783262,"uid":55519,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"終於有呢啲新聞 佢地真係hea左"},{"pid":"dc8ed8f05aea75f7c789984009c7c46ca3d4042a","tid":783262,"uid":35307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:46:45.000Z","msg":"上次bad boy已經比人話唔齊<br />\n今次都仲係咁"},{"pid":"d632a4b00c095b8b35722356ecf62d16de877e95","tid":783262,"uid":94075,"like":14,"dislike":17,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T19:13:40.000Z","msg":"針完椰梨未 佢係表情唔多姐 又話佢黑面 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8e5d0bf79ce6828a37ed4a0d458c7cfea8cbbc","tid"